{"ja154:0.1":"Jataka ","ja154:0.2":"Dukanipata ","ja154:0.3":"Dalhavagga ","ja154:0.4":"4. Uragajataka ","ja154:1.1":"“Idhuraganam pavaro pavittho, ","ja154:1.2":"Selassa vannena pamokkhamiccham; ","ja154:1.3":"Brahmanca vannam apacayamano, ","ja154:1.4":"Bubhukkhito no vitarami bhottum”. ","ja154:2.1":"“So brahmagutto cirameva jiva, ","ja154:2.2":"Dibya ca te patubhavantu bhakkha; ","ja154:2.3":"Yo brahmavannam apacayamano, ","ja154:2.4":"Bubhukkhito no vitarasi bhottun”ti. ","ja154:3.1":"Uragajatakam catuttham. "}